<lb ed="I" n="0147b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0147b0101">大齊天保五年歲次甲戌四月丙辰朔
<lb ed="I" n="0147b02" type="honorific"/>二日丁巳。　天宮頌<app type="star" corresp="#0147004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">文</lem><rdg wit="【原】">攵</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0147b03" type="honorific"/>夫<note n="0147005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30833"/>＝至【史】</note><note n="0147005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30833"/>【佛拓】，至【史】</note><app n="0147005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">至</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30833"/></rdg></app>道沖靜。必資物以顯真。沈隱留像。
<lb ed="I" n="0147b04" type="honorific"/>因阿難以存形。須達捨金。感群迷以就
<lb ed="I" n="0147b05" type="honorific"/>正。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>以邑儀人等。故知大慈異興。<note n="0147006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨵁＝閻【史】</note><note n="0147006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨵁【佛拓】，閻【史】</note><app n="0147006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">閻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨵁</rdg></app>浮
<lb ed="I" n="0147b06" type="honorific"/>難<note n="0147007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䖏＝處【史】</note><note n="0147007" resp="ihp" type="mod">䖏【佛拓】，處【史】</note><app n="0147007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䖏</rdg></app>。磬竭家珍。敬崇三寶。造二寶塔。石
<lb ed="I" n="0147b07" type="honorific"/>像三區。上為　皇帝<note n="0147008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30834"/>＝永【史】</note><note n="0147008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30834"/>【佛拓】，永【史】</note><app n="0147008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">永</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30834"/></rdg></app>隆。百官朝慶。法
<lb ed="I" n="0147b08" type="honorific"/>　界有形。咸同斯<note n="0147009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30779"/>＝願【史】</note><note n="0147009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30779"/>【佛拓】，願【史】</note><app n="0147009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30779"/></rdg></app>。其詞曰　金柱一
<lb ed="I" n="0147b09" type="honorific"/>振。万侶俱張。同茲<app type="star" corresp="#0147002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30838"/></rdg></app>法。眾惠<note n="0147b0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0147b0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>常。一階
<lb ed="I" n="0147b10" type="honorific"/>超九。<app type="star" corresp="#0147008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">永</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30834"/></rdg></app>誤時亡。殊山寶石。異想神功。誤
<lb ed="I" n="0147b11" type="honorific"/>斯應狀。動現真容。虛來異顯。滅去難蹤。
